{"tid":1264201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 請即刻呼籲身邊嘅人登記做選民！已登記嘅都立即check下選民資格係咪仲有效！","createTime":"2019-06-28T14:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:13:09.000Z","uid":65368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49b6631c7b38085e9214ff9300afa2009a98ba0c","tid":1264201,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"請自己登記及即刻呼籲身邊嘅人登記做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已登記嘅都立即check下選民資格係咪仲有效！<br />\n<br />\n[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=66c297f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=aa035772\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=768d1db7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a51bd79f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=0048c30e\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=58875b08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / <a href=\"http://FAX.PLUS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFAX.PLUS&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f7fa129c\" target=\"_blank\">http://FAX.PLUS</a> 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=d55ffa2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n2016立法會選舉總投票人數都係二百萬人，反送中遊行嘅人如果全部出黎投票嘅話，足以完全改寫立法會！<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好忘記制度內抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d801421063e5d20ec470bc52f9c95de97276468e","tid":1264201,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"我仲未改地址<br />\n但其實係同一個選區<br />\n咁我幾時去改好?"},{"pid":"39e1d878c941af578a3068003ab968bf2da098f8","tid":1264201,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d801421063e5d20ec470bc52f9c95de97276468e","tid":1264201,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"我仲未改地址<br />\n但其實係同一個選區<br />\n咁我幾時去改好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"只要資格仲有效就得"},{"pid":"6bbe286f6244c018fe8cdecb0eea11b8551f0b2d","tid":1264201,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"自推！<br />\n多一個議員都好重要！！"},{"pid":"33b27fe7f2bbb7a7829efe580efe6cbed7244a35","tid":1264201,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"812271293c21d546e4fb967c882b5cfed4c2a8f8","tid":1264201,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:37:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb7bad1799f0a4c47c91400edf2c8f7246dea1d8","tid":1264201,"uid":72661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"選你老母咩選,屌你老母投票撚,制度內抗爭有用就唔撚洗出黎啦on9"},{"pid":"2883114963ef4ab7aee1a938295206aa35c555ca","tid":126420